column99:
Painter for construction job in Køge ( Or a crew ) 
 On behalf of our partner, we are looking for a candidate, or individuals for a fulltime long term project contract set for 2 years at a major construction site in Køge. This is a great opportunity to work in a ever and fast changing environment, where you are in charge of the success of the daily operations. 
 We offer accommodation & Free housing for this job if you come with a crew we can provide transport, and a good living standard 5minutes from the site. 
 The team we are looking for consist of the following type of candidate profile: 
 
 Painters, for indoor work. 
 Previous experience is req. 
 
 Job Tasks are as follows: 
 
 Paiting walls, panels, ceiling. 
 
 What we expect: 
 
 English, or Italian understanding 
 Willing to adapt to changes in the daily job tasks, if the need arises from our clie 
 
 The salary is favorable according to the collective agreement. 
 (All social benefits, and transport money included) 
 Startup is as soon as possible. 
 Work hours are during the day hours (Startup between 07.00-15.00, Fridays 14.30 (Overtime can happen, if you are interested in working extra) 
 MEGA FLEX A/S will handle all the practical paperwork and guarantee employment under good terms, as well as handle pension and holiday pay. In other words, all you need to focus on is delivering quality work at our partner. 
 Application: 
 Interested? If so, hit the “Ansøg/Apply” Button today, and create a profile in our system ASAP. We are having candidate interviews fluidly until the startup date. If you have any questions, feel free to send a mail to a.holm@megaflex.dk and attach your phone number and we will contact you immediately. 
   
 Note : if you are living in a foreign country and wish to come to Denmark to Work on this job, we can offer accommodation. 
 Accommodation is free of charge. 
 However we need to start up middel sized crews for this, we cannot take in 1 candidate at a time.
